info.author: Ryan Simpson
info.name: uitk
info.summary: uitk is a versatile package for managing user interfaces, widgets, and event handling in Python using PySide2. Using naming convention, the switchboard module provides a convenient way to load UI files, register custom widgets, manage slots and styles, and interact with widgets. It aims to simplify the development and management of complex user interfaces.
